### expected behaviour
when creating a new group at the same time that creating a new user it is not shown properly, see image

### actual behaviour
although both user and group are creating, the group field is not shown correctly.

### steps to reproduce
1. access to owncloud with an admin account 
2. access to users
3. create a new user and group
4. click on create
5. check that the new user has been created, however, the group field is shown empty. by refreshing it, it is shown correctly.

